<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>TWZ</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 14:32:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>VH-92 爱国者获得花岗岩白宫直升机停机坪将最终让 VH-3D 海王退役</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/vh-92-patriot-getting-granite-white-house-helipad-will-finally-allow-vh-3d-sea-king-to-retire</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在白宫草坪上着陆数十年后，“海军陆战队一号”将在直升机停机坪上运行，特朗普称 VH-92 的制造商正在为此付费。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/vh-92-patriot-getting-granite-white-house-helipad-will-finally-allow-vh-3d-sea-king-to-retire"&gt;VH-92 爱国者获得花岗岩白宫直升机停机坪将最终允许 VH-3D 海王退役&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:32:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/vh-92-patriot-getting-granite-white-house-helipad-will-finally-allow-vh-3d-sea-king-to-retire</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜护卫舰上机枪数量可笑</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/north-koreas-frigate-bristles-with-a-comical-number-of-machine-guns</link><description>&lt;p&gt;朝鲜的Kang Kon军舰在为金公恩举行的示威活动中进行了全面的机枪扫射。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/north-koreas-frigate-bristles-with-a-comical-number-of-machine-guns"&gt;朝鲜的护卫舰上装备着滑稽数量的机枪，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 23:18:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/north-koreas-frigate-bristles-with-a-comical-number-of-machine-guns</guid></item><item><title>加拿大选择德国 212 型潜艇来满足急需的舰队更新需求</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/canada-picks-german-type-212-submarine-for-badly-needed-fleet-renewal</link><description>&lt;p&gt;此次采购 12 艘舰艇是加拿大有史以来最大的国防采购之一，标志着加拿大与欧洲盟国加强军事合作的重大转变。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/canada-picks-german-type-212-submarine-for-badly-needed-fleet-renewal"&gt;加拿大挑选德国 212 型潜艇用于急需的舰队更新的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 19:59:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/canada-picks-german-type-212-submarine-for-badly-needed-fleet-renewal</guid></item><item><title>没有爱国者拦截机，乌克兰无法击落任何袭击基辅的弹道导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/out-of-patriot-interceptors-ukraine-cant-down-any-ballistic-missiles-striking-kyiv</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌克兰正试图让盟国捐赠更多的爱国者拦截弹，而此时导弹的供应量非常低且需求极大。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/out-of-patriot-interceptors-ukraine-cant-down-any-ballistic-missiles-striking-kyiv"&gt;没有爱国者拦截机，乌克兰无法击落任何袭击基辅的弹道导弹，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 19:05:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/out-of-patriot-interceptors-ukraine-cant-down-any-ballistic-missiles-striking-kyiv</guid></item><item><title>中国在太平洋进行的潜射弹道导弹试验意义重大</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/chinas-submarine-launched-ballistic-missile-test-in-the-pacific-is-a-big-deal</link><description>&lt;p&gt;中国一次极其罕见的潜射弹道导弹发射发出了明确的信号，并使北京迅速发展的战略武器库更加引人注目。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/chinas-submarine-launched-ballistic-missile-test-in-the-pacific-is-a-big-deal"&gt;中国在太平洋进行潜射弹道导弹试验是一件大事的帖子&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 18:15:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/chinas-submarine-launched-ballistic-missile-test-in-the-pacific-is-a-big-deal</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯 Tu-142 Bear 在与英国航母近距离遭遇时掉落声纳浮标</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/russian-tu-142-bear-drops-sonobuoys-during-close-encounter-with-british-carrier</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Tu-142 海上巡逻机刚刚飞离威尔士亲王号，同时部署潜艇探测声纳浮标，F-35 对其进行尾随。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/russian-tu-142-bear-drops-sonobuoys-during-close-encounter-with-british-carrier"&gt;俄罗斯 Tu-142 Bear 在与英国航母近距离接触时掉落声纳浮标的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 17:23:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/russian-tu-142-bear-drops-sonobuoys-during-close-encounter-with-british-carrier</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：美利坚合众国版 250 岁生日快乐！</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-happy-250th-birthday-united-states-of-america-edition</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国两个半世纪。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-happy-250th-birthday-united-states-of-america-edition"&gt;后邦克谈话：美利坚合众国版 250 岁生日快乐！&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 20:44:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-happy-250th-birthday-united-states-of-america-edition</guid></item><item><title>克里米亚俄罗斯空军基地的加固飞机掩体因乌克兰无人机袭击而受损（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/hardened-aircraft-shelters-at-russian-air-base-in-crimea-damaged-from-ukrainian-drone-strikes</link><description>&lt;p&gt;对萨基空军基地的无人机袭击是乌克兰最新行动的一部分，目的是让克里米亚尽可能不适合俄罗斯军队居住。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/hardened-aircraft-shelters-at-russian-air-base-in-crimea-damaged-from-ukrainian-drone-strikes"&gt;克里米亚俄罗斯空军基地的加固飞机掩体因乌克兰无人机袭击而受损（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 20:16:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/hardened-aircraft-shelters-at-russian-air-base-in-crimea-damaged-from-ukrainian-drone-strikes</guid></item><item><title>这就是即将飞越首都上空的庞大空中舰队</title><link>https://www.twz.com/space/this-is-the-massive-aerial-armada-that-is-about-to-fly-over-the-capital</link><description>&lt;p&gt;NASA 将带领一波又一波的飞机（从隐形轰炸机到 VIP 直升机）飞越购物中心，庆祝美国 250 岁生日。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/space/this-is-the-massive-aerial-armada-that-is-about-to-fly-over-the-capital"&gt;“这是即将飞越首都的大型空中舰队”&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 18:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/space/this-is-the-massive-aerial-armada-that-is-about-to-fly-over-the-capital</guid></item><item><title>英国皇家海军海上发射经过实战验证的 Nyan Kamikaze 无人机，预示着舰队的“混合”未来</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/royal-navys-sea-launch-of-combat-proven-nyan-kamikaze-drone-points-to-fleets-hybrid-future</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新的舰载打击能力的展示是在推进无人机在整个舰队中深度整合的计划之际进行的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/royal-navys-sea-launch-of-combat-proven-nyan-kamikaze-drone-points-to-fleets-hybrid-future"&gt;英国皇家海军海上发射经过战斗验证的 Nyan Kamikaze 无人机预示着舰队的“混合”未来&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 17:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/royal-navys-sea-launch-of-combat-proven-nyan-kamikaze-drone-points-to-fleets-hybrid-future</guid></item></channel></rss>